            2 Charitie is necessarie. For we must2. Charitie.


               
               Iames. 5, verse. 16. 
               praie one for another; and for our enimies, Matth. 6, verse. 14. Matth. 5, 44▪ Mark. 11, 25 Luk. 23, 34. as our Sauior doth counsaile vs, saieng, When ye stande praieng, forgiue, if yee haue ought against any man, that your Father also which is in Heauen, may forgiue you your trespasses, &amp;c, Againe the spirite of God saith, Eccle. 28, verse 3, &amp;c. 
