                  mend the depenes of this mysterie, didst ordaine this Sacrament in thy last supper being euen readie to go frō thy Disciples vnto thy passiō, the more depelie to fixe it in our harts,



that it neuer slip out of our minds, but dailie in faith, feare, and reuerence, be recorded; and remaine according to thine holie institution, whole and perfect without adding or diminishing from the same.
